  <?dbhtml filename="libxfontcache.html"?>

  <title>libXfontcache-&libxfontcache-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      FontCache is an extension that is used by X-TrueType to cache information
      about fonts.
    </para>

